VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.(query|execute)\(\s*`|\$where\s*:\s*|sequelize\.query\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:parameterize|prepare|sanitize|validate|escape && MISSING:test|spec|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects query construction patterns requiring injection review.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Vue SQL/NoSQL Injection Sink.
